<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-white sticky-top shadow-sm">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold text-primary" href="/"><i class="bi bi-heart-pulse-fill me-2"></i>HealthBridge</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/">Beranda</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#fitur">Layanan</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link btn btn-outline-primary ms-lg-3" href="/admin">Login Admin</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero-section text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-3">Solusi Kesehatan <br> Masyarakat Digital</h1>
            <p class="lead mb-5 px-md-5">Platform terintegrasi untuk melaporkan kondisi lingkungan, memantau tren penyakit, dan meningkatkan kualitas hidup masyarakat Bandung.</p>
            <a href="/lapor" class="btn btn-light btn-lg px-5 py-3 fw-bold text-primary rounded-pill">Buat Laporan Sekarang</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="fitur" class="py-5 bg-light">
        <div class="container py-5">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="fw-bold">Layanan Utama Kami</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">Dibangun dengan teknologi Cloud mutakhir untuk kecepatan dan keandalan[cite: 66, 67].</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 feature-card shadow-sm p-4">
                        <div class="icon-box mb-3 text-primary fs-1"><i class="bi bi-megaphone"></i></div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold">Pelaporan Lingkungan</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted small">Laporkan potensi wabah atau kondisi lingkungan tidak sehat langsung kepada pemerintah.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 feature-card shadow-sm p-4 bg-primary text-white">
                        <div class="icon-box mb-3 fs-1"><i class="bi bi-cloud-upload"></i></div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold text-white">Bukti Digital (S3)</h4>
                        <p class="small text-white-50">Setiap laporan didukung unggahan foto langsung ke AWS S3 untuk validasi data yang akurat[cite: 42, 64].</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card h-100 feature-card shadow-sm p-4">
                        <div class="icon-box mb-3 text-success fs-1"><i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i></div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold">Monitoring Penyakit</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted small">Data tersimpan aman di RDS untuk analisis tren kesehatan masyarakat secara real-time[cite: 41, 50].</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-5 bg-dark text-white text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <p class="mb-2 fw-bold">HealthBridge Application</p>
            <p class="small text-white-50">UTS Cloud Computing - GENAP 2024/2025 [cite: 14]</p>
            <hr class="w-25 mx-auto my-4 border-secondary">
            <p class="small mb-0">Nazwa Nur Salsa Bella (152023173)</p>
            <p class="small">Informatika - Itenas Bandung [cite: 1, 10]</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>